    <h3 class="header">
        ABOUT THE FEATURED SCHOLARS
    </h3>
    <p class="flow-text light">
        This page is a directory for current UNC scholars researching the American South utilizing various digital methodologies. Scholars come from a myriad of departments across campus and have different approaches and questions, but ultimately they are all
        interested in advancing our understanding of the South through digital methods.
    </p>


    <p class="flow-text light">
        We will highlight a scholar every couple of days as a way to introduce them individually. Keep an eye out for our first post!
    </p>
</div>
